{"tid":2509284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"19 歲男生藏士巴拿被控 警透露逃出校園者均以暴動罪拘捕","createTime":"2021-04-29T10:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T10:19:28.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c47c93026cfbeb8127c75b5d78ba1d364c2c541f","tid":2509284,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"前年11⽉理⼤圍城衝突期間，警員指稱有男生在理大外圍行人隧道跑出，在路軌附近將他拘捕後，搜出兩支⼠巴拿。男生被控管有非法⽤途⼯具罪，案件今於九龍城裁判法院開審。拘捕被告的警員供稱，案發時看見三名可疑男子從隧道跑出，並欲向他掟石，又丟下背包，故向他們發射了兩發橡膠子彈，三人隨即分頭逃走。其中被告欲沿路軌逃走，但遭截停，搜出兩個只有手指及手掌般長的⼠巴拿。警員又透露，當日上級指令要以暴動罪名拘捕任何從理大出來的人。<br />\n<br />\n胡稱，被告當時想沿路軌向何文田逃跑，疑人二號則沿山坡向康莊道跑，疑人三號則折返行人隧道內。逃跑期間，被告及疑人二號分別丟下自己的孭袋。胡於樓梯邊成功截停被告，<span class=\"red\">惟追捕過程中視線曾有十數秒離開被告。</span><br />\n<br />\n盤問下，辯方問胡有沒有被三人以碎石擲中，<span class=\"red\">胡稱三人其實沒有掟出石頭</span>。辯方再問如何得知他們手持的是碎石，胡僅稱：「我見到。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方再問當他發射橡膠子時，三人是在奔跑中還是正站立，<span class=\"red\">胡稱三人當時站立</span>。辯方即問：「佢哋企定定咁畀你射呀？」胡答是，並認為當時他們未分辦到哪條路可以安全離開。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官<span class=\"red\">梁嘉琪</span>裁定案件表證成立。"},{"pid":"4acbfcca2b29f5213c1784b2e4e1f2f8e55e51d6","tid":2509284,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/JAPBBPULJJDOFEJAH5SCDXG3MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FJAPBBPULJJDOFEJAH5SCDXG3MI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=0da1799c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FJAPBBPULJJDOFEJAH5SCDXG3MI%2F&h=86264197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/JAPBBPULJJDOFEJAH5SCDXG3MI/</a>"},{"pid":"55d62bf8daceb9e928b3dcfd5ac05a2ef3af1d3e","tid":2509284,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"表面成立 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過係呢個官⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ba7b11414c819df4423bab86c0f5de585813e8","tid":2509284,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"口供與警員記事冊不一 警：時間倉卒匆忙<br />\n<br />\n辯方亦質疑，警員稱被告執起碎石打算投擲的說法，與其警員記事冊所記錄的有出入，指出記事冊寫「執起地下雜物」，警員解釋指，當時「時間倉卒匆忙，無形容（雜物）係啲咩」，所以在口供補充。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，<span class=\"red\">在辯方不提供證供的前提下，只能建基於推論。</span>就控罪的法律觀點，控方指兩件被搜出的工具均可用作「非法入侵」，例如「扭開鎖、打爛玻璃」，又指案發時正值大規模示威，認為板手可用於「破壞、傷人用途」。案件押後至 6 月 17 日續審。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%89%B3%E6%89%8B-%E7%AE%A1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E8%A1%A8%E8%AD%89%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF-6-17-%E7%BA%8C%E5%AF%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%2589%25B3%25E6%2589%258B-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF-6-17-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25AF%25A9%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9ce70c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%2589%25B3%25E6%2589%258B-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF-6-17-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25AF%25A9%2F&h=de411091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%89%B3%E6%89%8B-%E7%AE%A1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E8%A1%A8%E8%AD%89%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF-6-17-%E7%BA%8C%E5%AF%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"ffe47984fea79d6bac9c22384b500164e64cd1dd","tid":2509284,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}